索尔福德小伙子俱乐部“正式得救”：“有一盏灯，永远不会熄灭” https://www.nme.com/news/music/salfords-lads-club-is-officially-saved-there-is-a-light-and-it-never-goes-out-3816779?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=索尔福德小伙子俱乐部已正式保存，那里有一盏灯，而且永远不会熄灭Liberty DunworthThu, 28 Nov 2024 12:21:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsFolkIndiePopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3816779 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年索尔福德小伙子俱乐部的航拍图" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>莫里西、诺埃尔·加拉格尔、格雷厄姆·纳什等数千人为拯救这座历史悠久的场馆捐款</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/salfords-lads-club-is-officially-saved-there-is-a-light-and-it-never-goes-out-3816779">索尔福德小伙子俱乐部被“正式拯救”的帖子：“有一盏灯，它永远不会熄灭”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年索尔福德小伙子俱乐部的航拍图" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Salford@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>继今年早些时候威胁关闭之后，索尔福德小伙子俱乐部已确认将继续开放。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/report-shows-disaster-facing-grassroots-music-venues-the-big-companies-and-arenas-are-now-going-to-have-to-answer-for-this-3576307">报告显示草根音乐场馆面临“灾难”：“大公司和场馆现在必须为此负责”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该青年中心由罗伯特·贝登堡 (Robert Baden-Powell) 于 1904 年在奥德萨尔 (Ordsall) 开设。最初它是一个男孩俱乐部，但现在向所有年轻人开放。</p><p>这里是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Smiths">史密斯</a>夫妇最著名的照片的拍摄地，并出现<em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/peaky-blinders">《浴血黑帮》</a> 、《哈利法克斯最后的探戈》、《比格斯夫人》、《冷脚》、《蓝色谋杀案</em>》等电视剧和电影中。</p><p>然而，上个月有报道称，由于成本上升和赠款资金减少，该标志性网站面临关闭的威胁。为了保持开放，它被迫在 11 月中旬之前筹集 25 万英镑，并呼吁社区支持。</p><p>现在，在 Instagram 上分享的最新消息中，该场馆已确认已达到所需的财务目标，现在将被允许继续照常运营。</p><p> “我们做到了！索尔福德男女俱乐部正式获救，”更新开始。 “感谢支持者的慷慨解囊，我们已经实现了 25 万英镑的目标，确保这座标志性建筑的大门始终向我们的年轻人和社区敞开。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DC6TqQ3uSoE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px